source:
TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Quest Sync<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
Able though he may be, there are some situations which Yazel Ahuatan the Able cannot resolve by himself.
※The crafting portion of this quest is recommended for Disciples of the Hand level 1 and above, and the battle portion for Disciples of War or Magic level 41 and above.
target:
TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Schwierigkeitsanpassung<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
※ Dieser Auftrag wird für Charaktere ab Stufe 41 als Krieger oder Magier und ab Stufe 1 als Handwerker empfohlen.

In Ehcatl hat Yazel Ahuatan einen dringenden Auftrag für dich.

source:
TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_SEQ_01<tab>Yazel Ahuatan has asked you to craft a bladder lining component so that he might mollify Methuli Cattlan. He has provided the materials, but the facilities are another matter; only those in Hyrstmill, under the care of Dametta, will do. Journey to the hamlet and request her permission.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level.
target:
TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_SEQ_01<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var><var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> Die Schwierigkeit des Auftrags wird an die aktuelle Stufe angepasst.

Yazel Ahuatan hat dich mit der Herstellung <var 32 ((Item)) 02 ((　8092)) 020302 /var> beauftragt. Bitte Dametta in Mühlenhain um Erlaubnis, ihre Arbeitsstätte nutzen zu dürfen.

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_SEQ_02<tab>Dametta is willing to grant you permission to use her facilities─provided you carry out a simple task in exchange. She has prepared a hearty meal for Paulemont, a Wood Wailer stationed at E<var 1F /var>Tatt's Spire. You need only deliver the meal and return with the sack which held her previous delivery. Alternatively, you could converse with the woman further and attempt to persuade her...but that approach may not end well.
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_SEQ_02<tab>Für die Benutzung ihrer Arbeitsstätte hat dich Dametta um einen Gefallen gebeten. Bringe <var 32 ((EventItem)) 06F61E89E1020502 /var> zu Paulemont an E-Tatts Wachturm!

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_SEQ_03<tab>Paulemont is relieved to receive the meal from someone other than Dametta for a change. He presses an empty sack into your hands and insists that you not forget to return it to his benefactor.
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_SEQ_03<tab>Paulemont hat sich sehr über das Proviantpaket gefreut und dir dafür das leere Paket der letzten Lieferung mitgegeben. Bringe <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E89E2020502 /var> zu Dametta zurück und gib ihr auch <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E89E0020502 /var>.

source:
TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_SEQ_04<tab>The sack serves both to inflame Dametta's passions and satisfy her requirements. With the materials provided to you by Yazel Ahuatan, synthesize a bladder lining component, and deliver it to him at Ehcatl.

※In the event that the status <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Facility Access: Production<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> wears off or the synthesis ends in failure, you may try again by speaking with Dametta.
target:
TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_SEQ_04<tab>Dametta hat dir erlaubt, ihre Arbeitsstätte zu benutzen. Verarbeite <var 32 ((Item)) 03 ((　8053)) 020502 /var> zu <var 32 ((Item)) 02 ((　8092)) 020402 /var> und bringe es zu Yazel Ahuatan in Ehcatl.

※ Sollte der Status <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Arbeitsstätte: Herstellung<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> enden oder <var 32 ((Item)) 03 ((　8053)) 020202 /var> verloren gehen, kannst du Dametta erneut um Hilfe bitten. Sie wird dir dann das Material und die Arbeitsstätte für einen neuen Versuch zur Verfügung stellen.

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_SEQ_05<tab>Yazel Ahuatan accepts your work with a mighty squa-hawk, certain that it will meet with Methuli's satisfaction. The most modest of Ixal's posterior shall remain pristine...until next he incurs the wrath of the Hard.
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_SEQ_05<tab>Du hast <var 32 ((Item)) 03 ((　8092)) 020502 /var> bei Yazel Ahuatan abgeliefert. Gerade noch rechtzeitig, bevor Methuli Cattlan die Geduld verloren und dem armen Yazel die Schwanzfedern gestutzt hätte. Wenn es um ihren Traum vom Fliegen geht, verstehen die Wolkengleiter von Ehcatl wirklich keinen Spaß.

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the handmade meal to Paulemont.
TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_TODO_02<tab>Present the empty meal sack and the bladder lining component materials to Dametta.
TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_TODO_03<tab><var 08 E3E802E803 ((Synthesize a bladder lining component)) ((Deliver the bladder lining component to Yazel Ahuatan the Able)) /var>.
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_TODO_03<tab><var 08 E3E802E803 ((Handwerker-Notizbuch (Wilder Stamm) St.1: <var 32 ((Item)) 02 ((　8092)) 020502 /var> herstellen)) ((Yazel Ahuatan <var 32 ((Item)) 03 ((　8092)) 020502 /var> bringen)) /var>

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_000<tab>Squa-hawk! The one who too would be able, come, <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> is! Then to Yazel, lend a hand, that we might both escape the claws of the Hard!
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_000<tab>Khaaa, khaaa! Stutzt Methuli Cattlan mir Schwanzfedern, wenn ich nicht besorg <var 32 ((Item)) 06 ((　8092)) 020502 /var>. Hilfst du mir, <var 08 E905 ((Federlose)) ((Federloser)) /var>?

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_010<tab>Pluck my posterior bare, she shall, if rings of metal for the bladder lining we do not provide!
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_010<tab>Pass auf! Um Ballonhülle zu stärken, wir müssen Metallring in Mitte setzen. Ich geb dir Material, khaa, und du machst Ring, klar?

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_020<tab>Pluck my posterior bare, she shall, if water-resistant paint for the bladder lining we do not provide!
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_020<tab>Pass auf! Brauchen wir Mittel zum Einwachsen der Ballonhülle, um sie gegen Wasser und Wind abzudichten. Geb ich dir Material, khaa, und du fertigst Wachs, klar?

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_030<tab>Pluck my posterior bare, she shall, if leather-backed plywood for the bladder lining we do not provide!
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_030<tab>Pass auf! Um Ballonhülle zu stärken, wir brauchen Stoff- und Lederteil. Geb ich dir Material, khaa, und du machst Bauteil, klar?

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_040<tab>Able to craft this component himself, Yazel is, were it not for Ehcatl's dearth of facilities. Squa-hawk! Those of Hyrstmill, suffice they shall, but welcome within their walls, Yazel is not. With featherless chatterbox, featherless <var 08 E905 ((craftswoman)) ((craftsman)) /var> should speak.
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_040<tab>Gehst du nach Mühlenhain und fragst federlose Dametta nach ihrer Arbeitsstätte. Die ist genau richtig für Herstellung von <var 32 ((Item)) 06 ((　8092)) 020402 /var>. Schnell, schnell, meine Schwanzfedern sind in Gefahr!

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_050<tab>Highly unattractive, Yazel's posterior would be, if plucked bare of feathers. For the sake of Ixali maidens, with my materials and the featherless chatterbox's facilities, craft the component we require! Squa-hawk!
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_050<tab>Khaa, gehst du nach Mühlenhain und machst <var 32 ((Item)) 06 ((　8092)) 020402 /var> bei Damettas Arbeitsstätte. Khaa, khaa, schnell, meine Schwanzfedern sind in Gefahr!

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_060<tab>I know that look─you've a mind to use these facilities, don't you? It's hardly the first time, suffice it to say. I find it quite flattering, actually─and who wouldn't? That the facilities I've worked so hard to maintain are in such high demand is high praise indeed!
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_060<tab>Ja, aber natürlich kannst du meine Arbeitsstätte benutzen.

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_061<tab>However! That same demand means that I cannot allow unrestricted access, I'm sorry to say. Oh, don't look at me like that! Can you imagine the state they would be in if I let every traveler have the run of the place? It'd be no better than a pigsty!
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_061<tab>Darf ich dich vorher um einen kleinen Gefallen bitten? Ich müsste dringend ein Proviantpaket ausliefern, aber neuerdings kann sich eine alte Frau ja nicht mehr alleine in den Wald trauen.

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_062<tab>But worry not! You may use them if you take this lunch to Paulemont at E<var 1F /var>Tatt's Spire. A simple delivery should be no trouble for a strapping adventurer like yourself! Oh, and do remember to bring me any empty containers he may have. I reuse them, you see. One must <var 1A 02 /var>never<var 1A 01 /var> be wasteful!
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_062<tab>Sei so gut und bring das Proviantpaket für mich zu Paulemont an E-Tatts Wachturm. Er wird dir bestimmt <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E89E2020502 /var> von der letzten Lieferung mitgeben. Bring es mir bitte zurück, ja?

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_070<tab>Paulemont never leaves his post, so I've no doubt you'll find him at E<var 1F /var>Tatt's Spire. Nevertheless, I pray you don't take too long to deliver it! Meals are always best served fresh!
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_070<tab>Ach, du möchtest noch ein Schwätzchen halten? Aber gerne doch! Die Proviantlieferung eilt ja nicht.

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_071<tab>Such a dedicated Wailer, Paulemont is─and kind, too! I used to send him Mun<var 1F /var>Tuy tonic, and do you know what he did? He shared it with his comrades when supplies ran low!
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_071<tab>Paulemont ist ja so ein fleißiger Soldat. Unermüdlich hält er vor dem Turm Wache, als müsste er niemals schlafen. Zur Stärkung mache ich ihm immer leckeres Essen und frische Mun-Tuy-Milch.

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_072<tab>Just between you and me, he's quite handsome too! Much more than my husband, that's for sure. Oh, but don't go getting any ideas─I'd never do anything <var 1A 02 /var>indecent<var 1A 01 /var>. But a woman has eyes, you know!
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_072<tab>Beides schmeckt ihm immer so gut und gibt ihm Kraft! Ach, was für ein Prachtkerl. Viel stattlicher als mein Mann, der alte Tunichtgut!

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_073<tab>Like the other day, when a horde of ravenous opo<var 1F /var>opos burst through the gates and began raiding our storehouses, a party of courageous adventurers came to our defense. So strong and skilled they were─and <var 1A 02 /var>fetching<var 1A 01 /var> too! One young man in particular had such <var 1A 02 /var>lovely<var 1A 01 /var> arms, and for a moment I couldn't help but imagine them wrapped around me...
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_073<tab>Ach ja, und die Opo-Opos mal wieder ... ganz schön frech, die Biester ... kann man sich ja nicht bieten lassen ... und überhaupt ... <blablabla>

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_SYSTEM_100_073<tab>As Dametta continues to wax poetic about various men, your mind begins to wander...
TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_PAULEMONT_000_080<tab>Gods save me, today's the day, isn't it? She'll be here any moment...
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_PAULEMONT_000_080<tab>Entschuldige mein lautes Magenknurren. Ich warte auf Proviant von Dametta. Diesmal lässt sie ganz schön auf sich warten. Sie ist ja eine herzensgute Frau, aber leider auch sehr geschwätzig. Vermutlich kann sie sich mal wieder nicht losreißen.

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_PAULEMONT_000_081<tab>Is that from Dametta? I, uh... Thank you! Here, don't forget this! No need for her to come all this way to fetch an empty sack, am I right?
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_PAULEMONT_000_081<tab>Ach, das ist ja klasse! Endlich etwas zu essen! Kannst du das leere Proviantpaket vom letzten Mal gleich mitnehmen und zu Dametta bringen?

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_PAULEMONT_000_090<tab>All things considered, it could be far worse. At least she's not forcing that gods-awful tonic on me anymore.
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_PAULEMONT_000_090<tab>Danke für das Essen! Bring bitte das leere Proviantpaket zu Dametta, ja?

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_100<tab>I do so hope Paulemont wasn't disappointed that I couldn't deliver his meal in person. I trust you've brought the empty sack? Oh, and as a precaution, I must ask that you present your materials for inspection as well. You would be <var 1A 02 /var>shocked<var 1A 01 /var> by what some people have tried to make here, believe me!
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_100<tab>Und, hat es dem guten Jungen geschmeckt? Hoffentlich hat er dir <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E89E2020502 /var> mitgegeben. Gib es mir bitte, ja? Ach ja, zeig mir bitte auch das Material, das du verarbeiten möchtest! Dann bereite ich die Arbeitsstätte vor.

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_101<tab>My word, would you look how spotless it is! Nothing more satisfying than seeing that your man─ahem, that your <var 1A 02 /var>friend<var 1A 01 /var> didn't leave a single crumb. Ahem. Ah, yes, your materials! Though unusual, I don't believe they could be used for evil ends. Here you are. You'll note I didn't return them all─there are several times the required materials, it would seem. Whoever entrusted this task to you left a note in the bag: “To featherless neuker, give only required parts. In case of failure, retain spares.” Hmmm... What in the world is a “neuker”?
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_101<tab>Ja, das Material taugt etwas, keine Frage. Bitte, fang ruhig an! Die Arbeitsstätte ist bereit!

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_110<tab>Oh, do you require more time with the facilities? By all means, take as long as you like! And if you require additional materials, let me know. I have plenty here for the “featherless neuker.”
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_000_110<tab>Falls das Material nicht reicht oder du mit der Arbeitsstätte nicht zurechtkommst, dann frag mich einfach. Ich bin sicher, wir kriegen das hin.

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_100_100<tab>Is that the finished product? I...I have no idea what that is, but it looks splendid! I'm sure your client will love it! Ah─it so happens there was another note in the bag: “Retain spare parts, in case featherless neuker loses component en route.” He really doesn't trust you, does he?
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_DAMETTA_100_100<tab>Na, bist du fertig mit der Arbeit? Dann lass deinen Auftraggeber nicht länger warten! Falls du den Gegenstand verlieren solltest und neu anfertigen musst, kannst du dich gerne wieder bei mir melden.

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_130<tab>Feathered, my precious posterior yet is, but not for long if featherless <var 08 E905 ((craftswoman)) ((craftsman)) /var> does not deliver bladder lining component!

TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_131<tab>Squa-hawk! A gift to the Ehcatl, your craftsmanship is, and a gift to Ixali maidens, Yazel remains! Ah─ Squahaha! Naught more than jest, my words are, of course. Never would Methuli harm his tailfeathers, Yazel knows.
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_131<tab>Danke! Meine Schwanzfedern sind gerettet. Methuli wird sie mir nicht mehr stutzen vor Ungeduld!

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_132<tab>(A buzzard to be feared, the Hard is. Ware her claws, lest you suffer her wrath as I have!)
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_YAZELAHUATAN_000_132<tab>Mit Methuli ist nicht zu spaßen, wirklich nicht! Vor allem, wenn's um unseren Traum geht!

source: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_POPMESSAGE_000_200<tab>You now have access to the crafting facility.
target: TEXT_BANIXA102_01495_POPMESSAGE_000_200<tab>Die Arbeitsstätte steht dir jetzt zur Verfügung.
